lead_paragraph: Victor Martinez went 2 for 2 with a double, raising his average to .412, and Ian Kinsler also doubled as the Detroit Tigers beat the Tampa Bay Rays 6-5 Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Martinez Has 2 Hits as Tigers Beat Rays 6-5
